Package: funDE
Type: Package
Title: Functional Differential Expression Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Kai", "Guo", 
           email = "guokai8@gmail.com", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
    )
Description: Differential expression analysis at multiple functional levels 
    including genes, gene families, and pathways. Provides a unified framework 
    for bulk and single-cell RNA-seq with methods for aggregation, pathway 
    activity scoring, custom enrichment testing, and multi-level integration. 
    Enables detection of coordinated regulation and functional changes through 
    gene set analysis.
